# c/MessageSystem

Sub.Listener: "c/MessageListener_Dispatcher, c/MessageListener_Override"
ApproxDuration: ""
DependsOn: "c/Entity"

# Description
class Message;
class MessageBox { list<Message*> };
Entity { MessageBox };

The Entity can push new Messages into his own MessageBox.
The "game" can poll these Messages.
Every Message has a field in which it can define, when to poll it.

